#: ui/screens/end_screen/EndScreen.tscn
msgid "Not only did you learn the foundations of coding, you’re a big step closer to making your own games."
msgstr "មិនត្រឹមតែអ្នកបានរៀនគោលការណ៍គ្រឹះនៃការសរសេរកូដប៉ុណ្ណោះទេ អ្នកក៏បានឈានជិតមួយជំហានធំទៀត ក្នុងការអភិវឌ្ឍហ្គេមផ្ទាល់ខ្លួន។"

#: ui/screens/end_screen/EndScreen.tscn
msgid "Don't stop here..."
msgstr "កុំឈប់ត្រឹមនេះ..."

#: ui/screens/end_screen/EndScreen.tscn
msgid "The fun stuff starts now!"
msgstr "រឿងសប្បាយៗ ចាប់ផ្តើមឥឡូវនេះ!"

#: ui/screens/end_screen/EndScreen.tscn
msgid "There are 2 pathways learners traditionally take from here:"
msgstr "មានផ្លូវ 2 ដែលអ្នករៀនជាទូទៅជ្រើសរើសពីចំណុចនេះ៖"

#: ui/screens/end_screen/EndScreen.tscn
msgid "Following video tutorials"
msgstr "ការអនុវត្តតាមវីដេអូបង្រៀន"

#: ui/screens/end_screen/EndScreen.tscn
msgid "They’re a great way to pick up specific game mechanics but they’re not as effective when you’re trying to learn new skills from the ground up."
msgstr "វាល្អសម្រាប់រៀនច្បាប់ហ្គេមជាក់លាក់ ប៉ុន្តែមិនសូវមានប្រសិទ្ធភាពទេ បើអ្នកចង់ចាប់ផ្តើមរៀនពីសូន្យ។"

#: ui/screens/end_screen/EndScreen.tscn
msgid "• There’s no clear learning path."
msgstr "• គ្មានផ្លូវសិក្សា ច្បាស់លាស់។"

#: ui/screens/end_screen/EndScreen.tscn
msgid "• Retention and skill acquisition is slow and limited."
msgstr "• ការចងចាំ និងការទទួលបាន ជំនាញមានភាពយឺតយ៉ាវ និងមានកម្រិត។"

#: ui/screens/end_screen/EndScreen.tscn
msgid "We make our fair share of [b][color=#ebc3ff][url=https://www.youtube.com/@Gdquest/videos]free tutorials[/url][/color][/b]. They will come in very handy once you start making games on your own. But to get started, we really recommend you learn how to think like a game developer using [b][color=#ebc3ff][url=https://school.gdquest.com/godot-4-early-access]courses[/url][/color][/b]."
msgstr "យើង បង្កើត [b][color=#ebc3ff][url=https://www.youtube.com/@Gdquest/videos]វីដេអូបង្រៀន ដោយឥតគិតថ្លៃ[/url][/color][/b] ជាច្រើន។ ពួកវានឹងមានប្រយោជន៍ ខ្លាំងណាស់នៅពេលអ្នកចាប់ផ្តើមបង្កើតហ្គេមដោយខ្លួនឯង។ ប៉ុន្តែដើម្បីចាប់ផ្តើម យើងពិតជាណែនាំឱ្យអ្នករៀនពីរបៀបគិតដូចជាអ្នកបង្កើតហ្គេម ដោយប្រើ [b][color=#ebc3ff][url=https://school.gdquest.com/godot-4-early-access]វគ្គសិក្សា[/url][/color][/b]។"

#: ui/screens/end_screen/EndScreen.tscn
msgid "Learning with courses"
msgstr "ការរៀន ជាមួយ វគ្គសិក្សា"

#: ui/screens/end_screen/EndScreen.tscn
msgid "Note that most available courses online are actually premium series of video tutorials. The problem of retaining information and acquiring real skills unfortunately still applies to them."
